Name: Kings Of Wings
About the game: A story about dignity... A young, ambitious pigeon named Lord Crumbs seeks to stop pigeons from being a joke. In order to do this, there's only one true way of earning respect amongst bird kind... through the Kings of Wings Tournament! A very, very, veeeery dangerous survival race in which only the best of the best can get to the top. In order to become the most respected bird in history, Lord Crumbs must defeat: Chuck: A little but energic chick. Mr. Killer: A ferocious vulture. Dr. Penguin: The smartest bird alive. The Boss: The mighty and powerful eagle, who's dominated the tournament for centuries. Can Lord Crumbs get to the top or will he reaffirm that pigeons are nothing but jokes?
